msgstr "<a id=\"cryptography\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "State-of-the-art cryptographic tools\n"
msgstr "最先进的密码学工具\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails also comes with a selection of tools to protect your data using strong "
"encryption:"
msgstr "Tails 也预载了一些工具选项以利用强大的加密功能来保护用户的资料:"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"[[Encrypt your USB sticks or external hard-disks|doc/encryption_and_privacy/"
"encrypted_volumes]] using <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia LUKS]]</"
"span>, the Linux standard for disk-encryption."
msgstr ""
"[[加密USB随身碟或是外接硬碟|doc/encryption_and_privacy/encrypted_volumes]] 可"
"使用 <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia　LUKS]]</span>, 它是Linux上的磁"
"区加密标准。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Automatically use HTTPS to encrypt all your communications to a number of "
"major websites using [HTTPS Everywhere](https://www.eff.org/https-"
"everywhere), a Firefox extension developed by the [Electronic Frontier "
"Foundation](https://www.eff.org)."
msgstr ""
"自动地采用[HTTPS Everywhere](https://www.eff.org/https-everywhere)来加密上网"
"浏览的通讯. HTTPS Everywhere 是Firefox的外加元件，其由[电子前锋基金会 "
"Electronic Frontier Foundation](https://www.eff.org) 所开发。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Encrypt and sign your emails and documents using the *de facto* standard "
"<span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia OpenPGP]]</span> either from Tails "
"email client, text editor or file browser."
msgstr ""
"使用*实质* 标准的 <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia_de OpenPGP]]</span>"
"来加密和签署电子邮件和文档,不管是透过Tails上面的E-Mail客户端软体, 文件编辑程"
"式或是档案管理员程式."

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Protect your instant messaging conversations using <span class=\"definition"
"\">[[!wikipedia Off-the-Record_Messaging desc=\"OTR\"]]</span>, a "
"cryptographic tool that provides encryption, authentication and deniability."
msgstr ""
"保护网路即时通讯的交谈内容，请使用 <span class=\"definition\">[[!"
"wikipedia_de Off-the-Record_Messaging desc=\"OTR\"]]</span> -它是一种密码学工"
"具可以用来加密、认证与否决。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"[[Securely delete your files|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion]] "
"and clean your diskspace using [[Nautilus Wipe|http://wipetools.tuxfamily."
"org/nautilus-wipe.html]]."
msgstr ""
"[[安全地删除你的档案|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion]] 以及利用"
"[[Nautilus Wipe|http://wipetools.tuxfamily.org/nautilus-wipe.html]]来清理磁"
"碟 ."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[[Read more about those tools in the documentation.|doc/"
"encryption_and_privacy]]"
msgstr "[[从文档中进一步了解这些工具.|doc/encryption_and_privacy]]"

